Color
SIZE

Gender-free sizing.

This piece was designed to be part of your essential lamarel wardrobe. It is made from 100% GOTS certified organic cotton which is a soft and a chemical-free fabric.

Please note that organic cotton garments shrink a little bit after the first wash.

Designed in Switzerland and made in Portugal, because we care about who makes our clothes just as much as who we make them for.

Composition & Care

100% organic cotton

Fluffy inside (fleece)

Our labels are 100% organic cotton.
Our product packaging is bio-degradable and made in Spain. Once opened, please put it in a compost facility to allow total disappearance.
Our hang tags are printed on recycled paper.

Care instructions:
Machine wash cold
Do not bleach
Do not tumble dry
Iron low
Do not dry clean
Wash separately
Wash inside out

Shipping

Please note that everything will be sent within 7-8 days. We are a small business and everything is packed in-house with love, please be patient with us.

Once we ship your order, you will receive an e-mail with the tracking number confirming that your order has been shipped.
